description: Number of self-complementary directed 2-multigraphs with loops on n nodes.
comments: A 2-multigraph is similar to an ordinary graph except there are 0, 1 or 2 edges between any two nodes (self-loops are not allowed).
references: V. Jovovic, On the number of m-place relations (in Russian), Logiko-algebraicheskie konstruktsii, Tver, 1992, 59-66.
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Jan 21 2000
